Package: scruff
Title: Single Cell RNA-Seq UMI Filtering Facilitator (scruff)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Zhe", "Wang", email = "zhe@bu.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Demultiplex single cell RNA-seq fastq files, align reads to reference genome using Rsubread, and generate transcript count matrices with UMI filtering.
